ORG: ASIPONA Vallarta, Air Canada, Bliss, CJNG, La Jornada, Mexico News Daily, Southwest, United, Vallarta Adventures, WestJet, the Jalisco New Generation Cartel
PERSON: Claude, El Mencho, Juan Pablo Martínez Torres, Nemesio Rubén, Oseguera Cervantes
